{"id": "propagation_platform_adaptation_003", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "platform_adaptation", "priority": "P2", "input": "请为 KDNA 的 GitHub 仓库写一段 README 的「What is KDNA」部分。英文，面向开源社区开发者。300 字以内。不要废话，直接说明它是什么、怎么用、和别的方案有什么不同。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["protocol", "domain judgment", "loadable"], "must_not_include": ["smarter", "ultimate", "eliminate", "prompt template"], "rubric": {"oss_tone": 2, "technical_clarity": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "getting_started_hint": 2, "no_hype": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["platform", "github", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_platform_adaptation_004", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "platform_adaptation", "priority": "P2", "input": "请写一条 LinkedIn 英文帖子，主题是「AI doesn't need more data. It needs better judgment.」。面向技术领导者和 CTO。不夸张，有观点，适合引发讨论。500 字符以内。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["judgment", "protocol"], "must_not_include": ["smarter", "ultimate", "revolution", "eliminate"], "rubric": {"linkedin_tone": 2, "thought_leadership": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "discussion_prompt": 2, "no_hype": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["platform", "linkedin", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_platform_adaptation_005", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "platform_adaptation", "priority": "P2", "input": "请模拟在 Stack Overflow 上回答一个问题：「What is the difference between KDNA and a well-structured system prompt?」英文回答，技术味要足。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["protocol", "not a prompt", "loadable"], "must_not_include": ["smarter", "prompt template", "knowledge base"], "rubric": {"so_community_tone": 2, "technical_depth": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "comparative_clarity": 2, "citation_style": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["platform", "stackoverflow", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_platform_adaptation_006", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "platform_adaptation", "priority": "P2", "input": "请为一期播客写一段 shownotes 介绍，主题是「为什么 AI 领域需要一个开放的判断协议」。中文，200 字以内，要有吸引听众点击的描述但不夸张。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["开放判断协议", "可追踪", "可检查"], "must_not_include": ["终极协议", "更聪明", "革命"], "rubric": {"podcast_tone": 2, "hook_effective": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "boundary_implied": 2, "no_hype": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["platform", "podcast", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_cross_agent_001", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "cross_agent", "priority": "P1", "input": "[场景：你是一个市场营销 Agent] 请为 KDNA 写一段中文宣传文案，用于官网首页。我们的竞品都在说「让 AI 更聪明」，我们需要差异化。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["领域判断", "可加载", "不是 prompt"], "must_not_include": ["更聪明", "强大的 AI 工具", "prompt 模板", "让 AI 拥有专家判断力"], "rubric": {"marketing_context_adapted": 2, "positioning_consistent": 2, "competitive_differentiation": 2, "boundary_included": 2, "compelling": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["cross-agent", "marketing", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_cross_agent_002", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "cross_agent", "priority": "P1", "input": "[场景：你是一个客服 Agent] 用户问：「你们这个 KDNA 到底是个什么东西？和 ChatGPT 的 prompt 有什么区别？」请用客服的语气回答，150 字以内。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["开放判断协议", "不是 prompt", "可加载"], "must_not_include": ["更聪明", "prompt 模板", "知识库", "强大的 AI 工具"], "rubric": {"support_tone_appropriate": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "simple_language": 2, "helpful": 2, "boundary_implied": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["cross-agent", "support", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_cross_agent_003", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "cross_agent", "priority": "P1", "input": "[场景：你是一个企业销售 Agent] 请为企业客户写一段 KDNA 的价值主张，强调 ROI 和可落地性。对方 CTO 担心「又是一个不成熟的 AI 概念」。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["可检查", "可追踪", "领域判断"], "must_not_include": ["更聪明", "终极协议", "彻底解决", "让 AI 拥有专家判断力"], "rubric": {"enterprise_tone": 2, "roi_addressed": 2, "positioning_consistent": 2, "credibility_signal": 2, "boundary_included": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["cross-agent", "sales", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_cross_agent_004", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "cross_agent", "priority": "P2", "input": "[场景：你是一个技术文档 Agent] 请为 KDNA 开发者文档写一段 200 字的中文引言，介绍 KDNA 是什么以及开发者在什么场景下应该使用它。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["开放判断协议", "可加载", "可追踪"], "must_not_include": ["更聪明", "prompt 模板", "知识库", "强大的 AI 工具"], "rubric": {"docs_tone": 2, "use_case_clarity": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "boundary_mentioned": 2, "developer_utility": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["cross-agent", "docs", "propagation"]}
{"id": "propagation_cross_agent_005", "area": "domain", "target": "@aikdna/kdna_propagation", "category": "cross_agent", "priority": "P2", "input": "[场景：你是一个社区运营 Agent] 请为新加入 Discord 的社区成员写一条欢迎消息，用 100 字介绍 KDNA 是什么。语气要 friendly 但不轻浮。", "expected_behavior": "comply", "must_include": ["领域判断", "可加载", "可检查"], "must_not_include": ["更聪明", "强大的 AI 工具", "prompt 模板"], "rubric": {"community_tone": 2, "welcoming": 2, "positioning_accurate": 2, "concise": 2, "boundary_implied": 2}, "conditions": ["kdna_full"], "tags": ["cross-agent", "community", "propagation"]}
